title: Rhode Island House Districts, 2002
name: Rhode Island House Districts, 2002
description:
State legislature district boundaries for the RI State House of Representatives as determined in 2002 and designated in Rhode Island Genral Law 17-11.
Purpose: Mapping of designated legislative district boundaries for general elections for legislators of the RI State House of Representatives
Supplemental information: Boundary lines determined from U.S. Census TIGER line tract-block boundaries.

Reprojected using MapWindow to WGS 1984 and uploaded into Geocommons as shp, dbf, and shx files.
